Sentencas: To improve the performance of the Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (GDC) electrolyte in a solid oxide fuel cell, it is necessary to block the electronic conduction due to Ce3+/Ce4+ transitions occurring at elevated temperatures.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In this work, a GDC/ScSZ double layer consisting of 50 nm GDC and 100 nm Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-delta (ScSZ) thin films were deposited on a dense GDC substrate by the pulsed laser deposition (PLD) technology.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The effectiveness of the double barrier layer in blocking the electronic conduction of the GDC electrolyte was investigated.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results showed that the ionic conductivity of GDC/ScSZ-GDC was slightly lower than that of GDC in the temperature range of 550-750 degrees C, but the difference gradually decreased with the increase in temperature.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: At 750 degrees C, the conductivity of GDC/ScSZ-GDC was 1.54 x 10-2 S center dot cm(-1), which was almost the same as that of GDC.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electronic conductivity of GDC/ScSZ-GDC was 1.28 x 10-4 S center dot cm(-1), which was lower than that of GDC.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The conductivity results showed that the ScSZ barrier layer can reduce electron transfer effectively.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: More obviously, the open-circuit voltage and the peak power density of the (NiO-GDC)|GDC/ScSZ-GDC|(LSCF-GDC) cell were higher than those of the (NiO-GDC)|GDC|(LSCFGDC) cell in the temperature range of 550-750 degrees C.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The superior performance of the GDC/ScSZ-GDC electrolyte is attributed to the ScSZ thin layer, which is effective in blocking the electronic conduction of the GDC electrolyte.
Titulo: Superior Electrochemical Performance of a Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ/Zr0.8Sc0.2O2-δ Thin Bilayer-Protected Gadolinium-Doped Ceria Electrolyte in Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
